User story:

As a user I can do:

1. Verse a computer of three difficulty settings
2. Verse another human on the same computer
3. Beat highscores (time taken/number of moves to beat the other player/computer of different difficulties)
	a. This means I will be able to enter my name
4. Set a time limit for each move.
5. Select SUPER CONNECT FOUR MODE as a game mode
6. Select coin colour (Prevent two players choosing the same colour)
7. To be assisted by a hint system when struggling
	a. Novice will have the hint ready for them whenever they need it
	b. Intermediate will have a limited amount of hints
	c. Expert will have no hints at all